data.description: Encanterra Trilogy Resort. This amazing home is faboulous as a primary or second home, nestled in the all ages section between the main resort and the Adult Pool/Art Studio/Pickle Ball/Gaming area. Includes an owners lockoff room/Office if you want to rent when not here. The Golf Course is world renowned The Resoort includes an indoor pool, lap pool, Two Outdoor Pools with restaurants Built in Hot Tub , Gym, Spa & Proshop. With 4 Bedrooms and 3 Bathrooms you have incrredible guest space including an additional Den. Landscaping is maintained by HOA Upgraded appliances and designer touches. Enjoy the Goodlife Seller is willing to provide concession of paying Social Membership Fee of $8,500.
